    <section id="datathon">
      <h1>
        Datathon
      </h1>

      <aside>
        A day of skill-building and data visualization in Boston's Innovation District
      </aside>

      <p>
        We invite you to join MAPC at <a href="events/datathon.ics">District Hall on Saturday, March 15th from 9-6</a> for a day of skill-building and data analysis. Learn new skills or reinforce existing ones in the morning, then form teams and work on your data challenge submissions in the afternoon. The Datathon is an inclusive event, like a hackathon but welcoming all skill sets.
      </p>

      <h3>
        <a name="the-morning"></a>
        The Morning
      </h3>

      <p>
        Our morning session series, "How to Win a Data Challenge", will feature a diverse collection of data-driven folks leading tutorials and skill-building sessions. Learn more about data analysis, GIS, user-oriented design, and software development in order to create compelling entries.
      </p>

      <p>
        The "How to Win a Data Challenge" speaker lineup will be announced soon.
      </p>

      <h3>
        <a name="the-afternoon"></a>
        The Afternoon
      </h3>

